<section class="sec reveal" id="privacy-summary" style="padding-top:36px;padding-bottom:36px;" aria-label="Plain-language summary">
  <div class="ct read read--doc">
    <div class="tldr-prose">
      <span class="eyebrow">The short version</span>
      <p>We collect only what we need to respond to you and deliver our services &mdash; your contact details, what you tell us about your business, and (during an engagement) access to your financial records. <strong>We don&rsquo;t sell your data, ever.</strong> We use it to do the work, communicate with you, and meet our legal obligations. During engagements, <strong>we work inside your own QuickBooks file</strong> &mdash; your data stays yours, and you can revoke our access anytime. We share data only with the service providers needed to run our business (and only under confidentiality terms), or when the law requires it. You have rights to access, correct, and delete your information. The full policy is below.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

